tool_description: Convert a WGS84 latitude and longitude to OSGB36 easting and northing (British National Grid).
title: WGS84 to OSGB36

api_list.name: WGS84 to OSGB36
api_list.description: Convert a WGS84 latitude and longitude to OSGB36 easting and northing (British National Grid).
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://wgs84-to-osgb36.p.rapidapi.com/wgs84ToOsgb36/{latitude}/{longitude}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "wgs84-to-osgb36.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
